interestingcomments.content: I did a course for medical students on the perception of the image in neurology ... it is not easy to see an image and it varies among individuals ! The system of image perception involves the eye, several nervous centers ... I say this because I feel that almost (and all) of you are passed to digital and the drift and deformation of the perception of the image has changed with the coming of digital ....
